r.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731672458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6735f014192f525898586d2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20year%20of%20slowing%20demand%20for%20their%20services%20and%20a%20series%20of%20missteps%2C%20this%20is%20how%20the%20Big%20Four%20firms%20measure%20up%20against%20each%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20Aircraft%20Hit%20By%20Technical%20Snag%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20Air%20Force%20Plane%20Sent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20aircraft%20suffered%20a%20technical%20snag%20at%20Deoghar%20in%20Jharkhand%20this%20afternoon%20and%20he%20left%20for%20Delhi%20on%20another%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20Plane%2C%20sent%20from%20New%20Delhi%2C%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20PM%20Modi%20was%20in%20the%20plane%2C%20which%20was%20about%20to%20take%20off%2C%20when%20the%20fault%20was%20detected%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20stop%20the%20aircraft%20at%20Deoghar.%20Attempts%20are%20also%20being%20made%20to%20rectify%20the%20fault%20in%20the%20aircraft%20before%20the%20IAF%20plane%20arrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20addressed%20two%20rallies%20in%20Jharkhand%20today%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20tribal%20icon%20Birsa%20Munda's%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20as%20Janjatiya%20Gaurav%20Diwas%2C%20and%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20round%20of%20polling%20for%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%2080%20km%20away%20from%20Deoghar%2C%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Godda%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20helicopter%20remained%20grounded%20for%2045%20minutes%20awaiting%20clearance%20from%20the%20air%20traffic%20control%2C%20prompting%20the%20Congress%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20delay%20was%20deliberate%20to%20disrupt%20the%20campaign%20schedule%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20PM's%20rally%20near%20Deoghar%2C%20suggesting%20that%20his%20event%20was%20being%20prioritised%20over%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20movements.%20The%20chopper%20was%20allowed%20to%20take%20off%2045%20minutes%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20rallies%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20PM%20Modi%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Reiterating%20his%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bshehzada%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(prince)%20jibe%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20Mr%20Gandhi%20of%20conspiring%20to%20scrap%20reservations%20for%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%20(OBC)%20communities%20to%20%26quot%3Bweaken%26quot%3B%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20dangerous%20intentions.%20The%20Congress'%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bshehzada%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20conspiring%20to%20scrap%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs.%20The%20prince's%20father%20had%20declared%20reservation%20as%20slavery%2C%20bonded%20labour%20but%20he%20was%20later%20defeated%20in%20elections.%20His%20father%20had%20issued%20advertisements%20to%20remove%20reservations...%20We%20will%20thwart%20any%20such%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20ruling%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20which%20is%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20helping%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20become%20permanent%20residents%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20a%20charge%20levelled%20by%20several%20other%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20rally%20in%20Godda%20district%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20pushed%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%2C%20claiming%20it%20would%20change%20the%20face%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCaste%20census%20is%20bound%20to%20happen...%20We%20will%20demolish%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20reservation%20ceiling%2C%20PM%20Modi%20can%20do%20whatever%20he%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20for%20the%2081-member%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20will%20take%20place%20on%20November%2020%20and%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20November%2023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731672420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fiv60kipg_modi_625x300_08_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-aircraft-hit-by-technical-snag-in-jharkhands-deoghar-7025742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20aircraft%20suffered%20a%20technical%20snag%20at%20Deoghar%20in%20Jharkhand%20this%20afternoon.%20The%20aircraft%20will%20now%20have%20to%20remain%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20the%20city%20until%20the%20technical%20fault%20is%20fixed%2C%20causing%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20PM's%20return%20to%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-aircraft-hit-by-technical-snag-in-jharkhands-deoghar-7025742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20is%20selling%20record%20numbers%20of%20cars%20in%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Changan%20cars%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67371cb7ede4eeae3927c7d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESales%20of%20Chinese%20cars%20have%20exploded%20in%20Russia%20since%202022.%3Cp%3ECostfoto%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20cars%20are%20selling%20at%20record%20levels%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompetition%20from%20European%2C%20Korean%2C%20and%20Japanese%20carmakers%20has%20vanished%20since%20Western%20sanctions%20were%20imposed%20on%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20automakers%20face%20increasing%20tariffs%20in%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20cars%20are%20selling%20at%20record%20levels%20in%20Russia%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Russian%20analytics%20agency%20Autostat%2C%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fd228a85c-248a-430d-afe5-2b93bbc9ba06%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20turned%20to%20Chinese%20autos%20from%20brands%20such%20as%20Chery%2C%20Geely%2C%20and%20Great%20Wall%20Motor%20after%20sanctions%20forced%20Western%20brands%20to%20stop%20doing%20business%20with%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%2C%20Korean%2C%20and%20Japanese%20carmakers%20had%20dominated%20the%20Russian%20market%20with%20a%2069%25%20share%2C%20per%20Autostat.%20However%2C%20since%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-ukraine-war-moscow-west-sanctions-inflation-gdp-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWestern%20sanctions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20imposed%20against%20Russia%20following%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20Autostat's%20data%20showed%20a%20steep%20decline%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20regions%20now%20hold%20just%208.5%25%20of%20the%20market%2C%20while%20Chinese%20carmakers%20such%20as%20have%20jumped%20from%209%25%20to%2057%25%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp