html%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erankings%20for%20greenhouse%20emissions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helped%20power%20its%20huge%20economic%20growth%20in%20recent%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20pledged%20that%20China%20would%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchinaeucn.com%2Fcarbon-neutrality-china%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520September%25202020%252C%2520president%2520Xi%2Ccarbon%2520neutrality%2520to%2520the%2520world.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20neutral%20by%202060%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it's%20on%20track%20this%20year%20to%20record%20its%20first%20drop%20in%20greenhouse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-meeting-us-climate-solar-panels-coal-power-energy-security-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemissions%20since%202016.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20China%20has%20pushed%20harder%20to%20produce%20its%20own%20green%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sell%20it%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20producer%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20solar%20panels%2C%20and%20the%20percentage%20of%20its%20energy%20coming%20from%20renewable%20sources%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Frenewables-2023%2Fexecutive-summary%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20rapidly%20growing.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20work%20brings%20practical%20and%20economic%20benefits.%20Analysts%20also%20point%20to%20other%20motives%20for%20Beijing's%20green%20push%3A%20influence%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20the%20Trump%20administration%20sees%20renewable%20energy%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20jobs%2C%20China%20is%20leveraging%20clean%20energy%20as%20part%20of%20a%20long-term%20strategic%20gambit%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Fchinas-belt-and-road-initiative-is-poised-to-transform-the-clean-energy-industry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaniel%20Araya%20of%20the%20Brookings%20Institute%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20in%202018.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3BBelt%20and%20Road%26quot%3B%20initiative%20to%20grow%20its%20global%20influence%2C%20has%20provided%20developing%20countries%20with%20renewable%20energy%20technologies%2C%20including%20wind%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreen%20tech%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20Xi's%20economic%20vision.%20While%20China%20has%20spent%20a%20decade%20trying%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20advanced%20economies%20in%20existing%20tech%20(like%20semiconductors)%2C%20it%20is%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20securing%20leadership%20in%20emerging%20industries%20like%20cleantech%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McElwee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20is%20paying%20off%2C%20with%20global%20demand%20for%20renewable%20energy%20production%20technologies%20predicted%20to%20surge%2C%20and%20China%20set%20to%20account%20for%2060%25%20of%20installed%20global%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fnews%2Fmassive-global-growth-of-renewables-to-2030-is-set-to-match-entire-power-capacity-of-major-economies-today-moving-world-closer-to-tripling-goal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOctober%20report%20by%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20lags%20China%20as%20a%20clean%20tech%20economic%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20explicit%20about%20his%20plans%20to%20repeal%20and%20otherwise%20roll%20back%20climate%20policies%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F09%2F05%2Ftrump-inflation-reduction-act-00177493%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20pledge%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20before%20the%20election%20to%20%26quot%3Brescind%20all%20unspent%20funds%26quot%3B%20from%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20which%20provided%20billions%20in%20funding%20for%20clean%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d064aeb1-2497-4d9c-b893-7e2c1b98241d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20China%20step%20up%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20doubts%20over%20how%20much%20China%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20an%20international%20leadership%20role%20on%20climate%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20wary%20of%20international%20agreements%20to%20tackle%20climate%20change%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20last%20year%20was%20accused%20by%20European%20officials%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenvironment%2Fchina-denies-reports-it-obstructed-g20-climate-discussions-2023-08-02%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChina%2520denies%2520reports%2520it%2520obstructed%2520G20%2520climate%2520discussions%2520%257C%2520Reuters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobstructing%20G20%20efforts%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20tackle%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssuming%20a%20leadership%20role%20would%20likely%20require%20China%20to%20send%20money%20to%20other%20countries%2C%20said%20Crowther.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20question%20for%20officials%20in%20Beijing%20will%20now%20turn%20to%20whether%20China%20wants%20to%20deepen%20its%20financial%20commitments%20to%20helping%20other%20countries%E2%80%94particularly%20emerging%20markets%E2%80%94accelerate%20their%20own%20energy%20transitions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrowther%20said%20the%20run%20up%20to%20next%20year's%20COP30%20summit%20in%20Brazil%20would%20provide%20clues%20of%20China's%20intentions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Xi%20may%20be%20more%20interested%20in%20cementing%20China's%20economic%20advantages%20than%20in%20concrete%20diplomatic%20pledges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20Beijing%20will%20try%20to%20boost%20its%20image%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20substance%20will%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McElwee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-belief-limate-crisis-scam-hands-advantage-china-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731670364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6735f12bfa0140cdd5635905%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-belief-limate-crisis-scam-hands-advantage-china-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20likely%20US%20departure%20from%20global%20climate-crisis%20efforts%20offers%20an%20opening%20for%20Bejing%2C%20a%20clean-tech%20giant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-belief-limate-crisis-scam-hands-advantage-china-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20ICC%20Rap%20For%20Pak%2C%20Champions%20Trophy%20Tour%20Won't%20Go%20To%20Pak-Occupied%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20decided%20to%20cancel%20the%20planned%20trophy%20tour%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20in%C2%A0Skardu%2C%20Murree%2C%20and%20Muzaffarabad%20-%20areas%20that%20fall%20within%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK).%20The%20decision%20comes%20after%20objections%20from%20the%C2%A0Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20regarding%20the%20tour%C2%A0itinerary%20shared%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB).%20A%20nationwide%20trophy%20tour%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20PCB%20from%20November%2016%20to%2024.%20However%2C%20ICC%20has%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%C2%A0Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20areas%20out%20of%20the%20tour.%20This%20decision%20came%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20controversy%20surrounding%20India's%20participation%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20after%20ICC%20informed%20the%20PCB%20that%20India%20will%20not%20be%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20officially%20asked%20for%20a%20written%20explanation%20from%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20over%20its%20decision%20not%20to%20send%20the%20Indian%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20reported%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20after%20BCCI%20verbally%20informed%20the%20ICC%20of%20its%20decision%20not%20to%20send%20the%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20next%20year's%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20requested%20the%20ICC%20to%20provide%20a%20copy%20of%20India's%20response%2C%20sources%20told%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20of%20receiving%20a%20written%20reply%2C%20Pakistan%20may%20seek%20substantial%20evidence%20supporting%20the%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20told%20Geo%20News%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20ICC%20would%20then%20have%20to%20take%20a%20final%20decision%20about%20India%20after%20reviewing%20those%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20also%20informed%20Geo%20News%20that%20if%20India%20fails%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3Bproper%20reasons%26quot%3B%20for%20not%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20then%20they%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20country%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20India%20refuses%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20then%20another%20team%20may%20come%20in%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20mega%20event%2C%20the%20sources%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20are%20the%20defending%20champions%20of%20the%20upcoming%20edition%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20Amid%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20India's%20participation%20and%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%C2%A0PCB%C2%A0revealed%20that%20the%20trophy%20tour%20for%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20will%20kick%20off%20from%20Islamabad%20on%20November%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20firmly%20held%20the%20stance%20of%20not%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20citing%20'security%20concerns'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20BCCI%20vice-president%20Rajeev%20Shukla%20stated%20that%20India%20would%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20only%20if%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20permitted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Pakistan%20hosted%20the%20Asian%20Trophy%2C%20but%20it%20was%20held%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20with%20India%20playing%20its%20matches%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20is%20also%20on%20the%20cards%2C%20but%20last%20week%2C%C2%A0PCB%C2%A0chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20claimed%20that%20there%20have%20been%20no%20talks%20about%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20in%20such%20a%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20sources%20reported%20that%20South%20Africa%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20emerged%20as%20possible%20venues%20for%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202025%20if%20Pakistan%20pulled%20out%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20tournament%20is%20shifted%2C%20there%20are%20also%20chances%20that%20Pakistan%20could%20withdraw%20from%20the%20tournament%20if%20ICC%20moves%20the%20tournament%20to%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731670260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F1rvvhgg_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_06_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbig-icc-rap-for-pakistan-champions-trophy-tour-wont-go-to-pak-occupied-ka