192f525898584b1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrittany%20Boals%20Moeller%20is%20one%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs's%20newest%20partners.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20named%2095%20partners%20last%20week%2C%20including%20private%20wealth%20exec%20Brittany%20Boals%20Moeller.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2039-year-old%20runs%20the%20Southeast%20region%20and%20leads%20strategy%20for%20young%20and%20women%20clients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20told%20BI%20how%20the%20bank%20is%20catering%20to%20these%20prized%20clients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Boals%20Moeller%2C%20one%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20newly%20minted%20partners%2C%20didn't%20picture%20a%20career%20in%20finance%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20bank%2017%20years%20ago.%20She%20grew%20up%20in%20Jonesboro%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20where%20her%20parents%20were%20professors%20at%20the%20local%20university.%20After%20graduating%20from%20New%20York%20University%20in%202007%2C%20she%20thought%20she%20would%20work%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20for%20a%20few%20years%20to%20save%20up%20for%20graduate%20school%2C%20perhaps%20to%20study%20public%20policy%20or%20become%20a%20lawyer.%20But%20even%20when%20the%20financial%20crisis%20hit%2C%20which%20was%20an%20opportune%20time%20to%20go%20back%20to%20school%2C%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Goldman%2C%20you%20are%20given%20tremendous%20responsibility%20and%20opportunity%20young%20in%20your%20career%20if%20you%20prove%20yourself%20able%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20once%20been%20bored%2C%20and%20so%20it's%20an%20easy%20choice%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20is%20based%20in%20Atlanta%20and%20runs%20the%20Southeast%20region%20of%20Goldman%20Sach's%20private%20wealth%20division.%20While%20wealth%20management%20clients%20skew%20older%2C%20the%20division%20has%20a%20pipeline%20of%20rich%20millennial%20founders%20who%20work%20with%20the%20investment%20banking%20arm.%20Boals%20Moeller%20said%20these%20clients%20in%20their%2030s%20and%2040s%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20want%20more%20than%20investment%20advice%2C%20desiring%20services%20like%20concierge%20healthcare%20and%20bill%20pay%20that%20make%20their%20lives%20easier.%20To%20keep%20these%20clients%20loyal%2C%20she%20leads%20an%20initiative%20to%20cater%20to%20younger%20clients%2C%20including%20heirs%20and%20self-made%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20another%20that%20focuses%20on%20women%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20busy.%20They%20want%20simplicity.%20They%20need%20good%20people%20around%20them%20to%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20dealmaking%20drought%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-private-wealth-management-asset-david-solomon-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewealth%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20business%20gained%20new%20prominence.%20%26quot%3BQuite%20frankly%2C%20private%20wealth%20management%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20has%20never%20been%20as%20much%20of%20a%20focus%20for%20the%20firm%20as%20it%20is%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20division%20cohead%20John%20Mallory%20told%20BI%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoals%20Moeller%20said%20the%20business's%20current%20stature%20is%20the%20result%20of%20investments%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20making.%20She%20served%20as%20chief%20of%20staff%20to%20wealth%20management%20head%20Tucker%20York%20during%20the%20financial%20crisis.%20Around%202010%2C%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20listening%20tour%20of%20every%20wealth%20office.%20The%20advisor%20feedback%20led%20to%20the%20bank%20expanding%20its%20offerings%20beyond%20investment%20and%20tax%20planning%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20this%20going%20way%20back%2C%20and%20it%20certainly%20continues%20today%2C%20which%20is%20we%20are%20not%20purely%20an%20investment%20solution%20for%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BInvestments%20are%20critical%20and%20core%20to%20our%20work%2C%20but%20increasingly%20we're%20seeing%20that%20with%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20wealth%20owners%20today%2C%20they%20are%20seeking%20simplicity%20and%20solutions%20in%20all%20aspects%20of%20their%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20family%20office%20offering%2C%20Apex%2C%20launched%20a%20few%20years%20later.%20Now%2C%20the%20division%20offers%20chief%20financial%20officer%20services%20to%20help%20clients%20with%20not%20just%20estate%20planning%20but%20also%20lifestyle%20services%20like%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECatering%20to%20these%20younger%20clients%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20old-money%20heirs%20or%20startup%20founders%20celebrating%20their%20first%20windfall%2C%20requires%20meeting%20them%20where%20they%20are.%20That%20usually%20isn't%20over%20a%20steak%20and%20martini%20lunch%20or%2018%20holes%20at%20the%20golf%20course.%20What%20entices%20these%20clients%20more%2C%20Boals%20Moeller%20said%2C%20is%20getting%20to%20meet%20like-minded%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20holds%20events%20and%20conferences%2C%20often%20with%20star-studded%20lineups%20or%20in%20scenic%20locales.%20In%20August%2C%20Boals%20Moeller%20hosted%20a%20reception%20in%20Atlanta%20with%20singer%20Ciara%20and%20Marc-Kwesi%20Farrell%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20rum%20brand%20that%20provided%20custom%20cocktails.%20In%20October%202023%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20hosted%20a%20conference%20in%20Deer%20Valley%20where%20billionaire%20Patr%C3%B3n%20founder%20John%20Paul%20DeJoria%20talked%20about%20keeping%20a%20business%20empire%20in%20the%20family.%20Sustainability%20and%20sports%20are%20particularly%20interesting%20to%20this%20demographic%2C%20with%20Goldman%20Sachs%20hosting%20a%20tour%20of%20a%20waste-to-clean-energy%20power%20plant%20in%20Copenhagen%20and%20bringing%20in%20Michelle%20Hynik%2C%20president%20of%20women's%20football%20club%20Utah%20Royals%2C%20to%20the%20Deer%20Valley%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvisors%20also%20introduce%20clients%20to%20each%20other%20when%20appropriate%2C%20such%20as%20a%20pre-IPO%20founder%20to%20an%20entrepreneur%20who%20has%20already%20been%20through%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20effort%20is%20put%20into%20helping%20people%20not%20only%20just%20manage%20the%20risk%20and%20obviously%20the%20investment%20side%20of%20things%2C%20but%20also%20the%20broader%20piece%2C%20which%20is%20how%20do%20we%20help%20you%20have%20an%20amazing%20corporate%20outcome%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20your%20business%2C%20and%20how%20do%20we%20help%20you%20as%20a%20family%20appropriately%20prepare%20for%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvisors%20can%20meet%20with%20families%20one-on-one%20for%20financial%20education.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20these%20millennial%20and%20Gen-Z%20clients%20prefer%20digital%20education%20on%20their%20own%20time.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20has%20courses%20for%20children%20of%20clients%20as%20early%20as%2015%20years%20old.%20This%20Semester%20at%20GS%20program%20has%20six%20one-hour%20sessions%20that%20span%20trading%20talks%20from%20executives%20in%20global%20markets%20as%20well%20as%20personal%20finance%20topics%20like%20how%20to%20think%20about%20a%20credit%20score.%20These%20virtual%20sessions%20are%20cameras%20off%2C%20Boals%20Moeller%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20at%20a%20desk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20another%20hour%20of%20homework.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-partner-brittany-boals-moeller-private-wealth-management-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731667322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67351c45192f525898584b1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2