-from-home-day-exacerbated-nightmare-delays-for-70k-travelers-report%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENY%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20problem%20grew%2C%20as%20some%20engineers%20were%20working%20from%20home%20that%20day%2C%20and%20were%20unable%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20remotely%20on%20time.%20An%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20a%20critical%20delay%20in%20resolving%20the%20issue%20was%20caused%20by%20difficulties%20in%20authenticating%20a%20remote%20engineer's%20password%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glitch%20began%20early%20on%20August%2028%2C%202023%2C%20and%20grounded%20flights%20nationwide.%20National%20Air%20Traffic%20Services%20(NATS)%20had%20arranged%20for%20a%20Level%202%20engineer%20to%20be%20available%20on%20call%2C%20but%20not%20on-site%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20exceptionally%20busy%20travel%20day.%20A%20Level%201%20engineer%2C%20who%20was%20present%20at%20NATS'%20Swanwick%20facility%20in%20Hampshire%2C%20immediately%20began%20diagnostic%20procedures%20after%20the%20systems%20failed%20at%208%3A32%20AM.%20However%2C%20the%20engineer%20struggled%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20because%20the%20senior%20technical%20support%20engineer%20was%20working%20remotely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remote%20engineer's%20attempts%20to%20log%20in%20and%20fix%20the%20issue%20were%20delayed%20after%20password%20authentication%20issues%20prevented%20timely%20access%20to%20the%20system.%20It%20took%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20for%20the%20engineers%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20but%20they%20still%20couldn't%20resolve%20the%20problem%20right%20away.%20The%20glitch%20wasn't%20fully%20fixed%20until%20four%20hours%20after%20it%20was%20first%20detected%20but%20not%20before%20causing%20disruptions%20to%20flight%20schedules%20that%20stretched%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripple%20effect%20of%20the%20disruption%20forced%20airlines%20to%20pay%20out%20over%20%24126%20million%20in%20compensation%20to%20affected%20travellers.%20The%