0wife%20Christine%20Hearst%20Schwarzman%20outside%20of%20the%20Met%20Gala.%20Steve%20is%20wearing%20white%20tie%20attire%2C%20and%20Christine%20is%20wearing%20a%20gold.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67363a16ede4eeae39279cb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Schwarzmans%20came%20dressed%20to%20impress%20at%20the%202022%20Met%20Gala%2C%20meeting%20the%20Gilded%20Age%20theme%20in%20a%20white%20tie%20and%20a%20gold%20dress.%3Cp%3ETheo%20Wargo%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20known%2C%20however%2C%20about%20how%20the%20private-equity%20titan%20manages%20his%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20conference%20last%20year%2C%20Schwarzman%20suggested%20that%20the%20firm%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-deal-to-expand-hq-in-latest-sign-of-growth-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecofounded%20in%201985%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20sufficient%20to%20handle%20his%20financial%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20own%20a%20lot%20of%20stock%2C%20and%20I%20invest%20in%20all%20of%20our%20funds%2C%20so%20the%20firm%20is%20my%20family%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwarzman%20said%20at%20the%20Bank%20of%20America%20Securities%20Financial%20Services%20gathering%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AlphaSense%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20learned%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Schwarzman%20also%20has%20a%20family%20office%20with%20a%20name%20that%20harkens%20back%20to%20his%20childhood.%20Pennypack%20is%20run%20by%20a%20former%20Blackstone%20tax%20expert%20and%20employs%20dozens%20of%20people%2C%20including%20housekeepers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20personal%20assistants%2C%20according%20to%20public%20records%20and%20conversations%20with%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20Schwarzman's%20money-management%20tactics%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20requested%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20about%20his%20private%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20secretive%2C%20with%20a%20nondisclosure%20agreement%20at%20the%20ready%20for%20its%20contractors%2C%20and%20provides%20support%20for%20at%20least%20some%20of%20Schwarzman's%20charitable%20organizations%20and%20political%20dealings.%20Pennypack%20also%20helps%20care%20for%20and%20manage%20many%20of%20the%20Schwarzman%20family's%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20manage%20billionaire%20Steve%20Schwarzman's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22061bb84c-1342-46df-a7e6-0fa5a6a820d1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20of%20Schwarzman's%20wealth%20is%20tied%20up%20in%20Blackstone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchwarzman%20cofounded%20Blackstone%20in%201985%20with%20his%20former%20boss%2C%20Pete%20Peterson%2C%20and%20%24400%2C000%20in%20seed%20money.%20Today%2C%20it%20manages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-third-quarter-earnings-private-credit-insurance-unit-aum-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20%241%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20alternative-asset%20manager%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20the%20biggest%20single%20shareholder%2C%20with%20a%2019%25%20stake%2C%20surpassing%20institutional%20giants%20like%20Vanguard.%20Based%20on%20a%20recent%20stock%20price%20of%20%24181.17%2C%20his%20stake%20is%20worth%20%2441.7%20billion%2C%20which%20means%20that%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20Schwarzman's%20wealth%20comes%20directly%20from%20his%20equity%20in%20Blackstone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20shareholder%2C%20Schwarzman%20also%20benefits%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-ceo-steve-schwarzman-earnings-in-2017-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecash%20dividends%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20pays%20its%20stock%20owners.%20Public%20records%20show%20that%20in%202023%2C%20he%20took%20home%20%24777%20million%20in%20dividends%2C%20a%2029%25%20decline%20from%20the%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20dividends%20he%20took%20home%20in%202022.%20Before%20Blackstone%20went%20public%2C%20Schwarzman%20received%20cash%20dividends%20as%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchwarzman%20is%20also%20the%20largest%20individual%20investor%20in%20Blackstone's%20funds%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20him%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Schwarzman%20is%20the%20largest%20individual%20investor%20in%20both%20Blackstone's%20stock%20and%20our%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20demonstrating%20his%20full%20alignment%20with%20the%20success%20of%20the%20firm%20and%20its%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20could%20find%20no%20evidence%20that%20Pennypack%20invests%20on%20behalf%20of%20Schwarzman%2C%20with%20no%20regulatory%20filings%20showing%20that%20it%20owns%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20unusual%20but%20not%20unheard%20of%2C%20Marc%20Sharpe%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Family%20Office%20Association%2C%20said.%20He%20pointed%20to%20Michael%20Dell%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Dell%20Computer%20who%20invests%20through%20MSD%20Capital%20but%20also%20has%20a%20separate%20office%20to%20manage%20and%20run%20his%20personal%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20single%20correct%20way%20to%20define%20a%20family%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharpe%20wrote%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOftentimes%2C%20they're%20described%20as%20a%20buffet%20menu%20of%20financial%20plus%20concierge%20services%20that%20wealthy%20families%20might%20utilize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237457fb4-3ead-4cc8-a639-7ed014e15612%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20name%20is%20linked%20to%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pennypack%20name%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20throwback%20to%20Schwarzman's%20youth.%20His%20family%20lived%20on%20Pennypack%20Road%20after%20moving%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20its%20neighboring%20suburbs%20when%20Schwarzman%20was%20a%20teenager.%20Property%20records%20show%20that%20his%20parents%20bought%20their%20home%2C%20which%20abuts%20Pennypack%20Creek%2C%20a%2022-mile%20creek%20that%20empties%20into%20the%20Delaware%20River%2C%20in%201960%20and%20sold%20it%20decades%20later%2C%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20railroad%20bridge%20over%20a%20river%2C%20surrounded%20by%20a%20forest%20in%20autumn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673666d4fa0140cdd563955a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223765%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20railroad%20bridge%20crossing%20over%20Pennypack%20Creek.%3Cp%3E%3A%20Education%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPennypack%20LLC%20was%20incorporated%20in%202018%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-done-with-delaware-other-corporations-unlikely-to-follow-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelaware%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20entity%20existed%20before%20in%20a%20different%20form%2C%20and%20representatives%20for%20Schwarzman%20declined%20to%20clarify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Blackstone's%202023%20annual%20report%2C%20it%20provides%20Schwarzman's%20family%20office%20with%20%26quot%3Boffices%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20Schwarzman%20is%20responsible%20for%20reimbursing%20Blackstone%20for%20the%20costs.%20Until%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20was%20registered%20to%20a%20Blackstone%20office%20address%2C%20according%20to%20corporate%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blackstone%20signage%20outside%20Blackstone%20Group%20headquarters%20in%20NYC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634e3c610dfcda409665f4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlackstone's%20NYC%20headquarters%3Cp%3EJeenah%20Moon%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20family%20offices%2C%20Pennypack%20is%20secretive.%20According%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-nondisclosure-agreements-silence-control-workers-silicon-valley-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENDA%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20vendors%20that%20work%20with%20Pennypack%2C%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20signees%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20disclose%20information%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BSchwarzman%20Group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20document%2C%20the%20Schwarzman%20Group%20includes%20%26quot%3Ball%20employees%20of%20Pennypack%2C%20all%20employees%20of%20all%20residences%20of%20Stephen%20A.%20Schwarzman%20and%2For%20Christine%20Hearst%20Schwarzman%20regardless%20of%20the%20location%20of%20such%20residences%3B%20and%20all%20business%20entities%20that%20Pennypack%20manages%2C%20operates%20or%20is%20associated%20with%2C%20and%20the%20employees%20and%20agents%20of%20those%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce719a95-bc69-41be-9292-52d9184d267d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20runs%20Pennypack%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPennypack%20is%20run%20by%20John%20Magliano%2C%20a%20former%20Blackstone%20executive%20and%20accountant.%20Magliano's%20LinkedIn%20profile%20says%20he%20has%20been%20the%20president%20of%20a%20family%20office%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20more%20than%2018%20years%20with%20Blackstone%2C%20including%20as%20the%20CFO%20of%20its%20private-equity%20group%2C%20which%20runs%20its%20control%20investments%20in%20businesses%2C%20and%20as%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20Blackstone's%20tax%20group%2C%20which%20helps%20prepare%20its%20tax%20returns%20and%20studies%20the%20tax%20implications%20of%20business%20decisions.%20After%20leaving%20to%20run%20Pennypack%2C%20Magliano%20stayed%20on%20as%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20Blackstone%20through%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchwarzman%20thanks%20Magliano%20in%20the%20acknowledgments%20section%20of%20his%20autobiography%2C%20along%20with%20Paul%20A.%20White%2C%20another%20Pennypack%20executive.%20The%20pair%20are%20listed%20as%20officers%20in%20LLCs%20tied%20to%20a%20string%20of%20Schwarzman's%20recent%20home%20purchases%2C%20including%20his%20%2432.5%20million%20purchase%20of%20a%20mansion%20on%20the%20tony%20Easton%20Street%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnantucket-homes-give-away-free-move-houses-cost-reason-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENantucket%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20marked%20the%20largest%20private-home%20sale%20in%20the%20island's%20history%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224212%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Postcard%20of%20the%20White%20Elephant%2C%20an%20iconic%20Nantucket%20hotel%2C%20with%20sailboats%20in%20front%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67366899192f52589858a9f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20old%20postcard%20of%20the%20White%20Elephant%20Hotel%2C%20an%20iconic%20Nantucket%20landmark%20nearby%20Schwarzman's%20harbor-side%20home.%3Cp%3ESepia%20Times%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20men%20are%20also%20named%20as%20officers%20of%20LLCs%20linked%20to%20the%20%2443%20million%20purchase%20and%20renovation%20of%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilded-age-mansions-photos-wealth-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20Newport%2C%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20mansions%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Ocean%20View%20and%20Miramar%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20Schwarzman%20said%20he%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.townandcountrymag.com%2Fsociety%2Fmoney-and-power%2Fa61852950%2Fsteve-schwarzman-miramar-private-museum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturn%20into%20a%20museum%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20dies.%20They%20are%20also%20