2TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20Killed%20Man%20Over%20Fight%20At%20Meat%20Shop%2C%20Then%20Calmly%20Walked%20Out%20With%20His%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Noida%2C%20a%20man's%20routine%20trip%20to%20buy%20meat%20on%20a%20quiet%20Thursday%20afternoon%20took%20a%20shocking%20turn%20as%20he%20was%20stabbed%20to%20death%20outside%20a%20shop.%20Shahzad%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20Meerut%20native%20living%20in%20Noida%2C%20and%20an%20unidentified%20customer%20had%20arrived%20at%20the%20shop%20owned%20by%20Gulzar.%20As%20the%20two%20awaited%20service%2C%20a%20seemingly%20benign%20argument%20over%20a%20towel%20spiralled%20into%20a%20deadly%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Shahzad%20asked%20the%20unknown%20man%20to%20lend%20him%20a%20towel%20he%20wore%2C%20the%20request%20provoked%20the%20accused%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20heated%20exchange.%20Eyewitnesses%20describe%20how%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20rising%20tempers%2C%20the%20attacker%20suddenly%20seized%20a%20butcher's%20knife%20lying%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20of%20the%20Sector%20117%20meatshop.%20Without%20hesitation%2C%20he%20plunged%20it%20into%20Shahzad's%20stomach%2C%20cutting%20it%20open%20which%20sent%20Shahzad%20staggering%20from%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20his%20bleeding%20stomach%2C%20Shahzad%20ran%20approximately%2040%20metres%20to%20a%20nearby%20intersection.%20His%20desperate%20plea%20for%20help%2C%20as%20he%20collapsed%20onto%20a%20culvert%2C%20went%20unanswered.%20The%20accused%20continued%20his%20pursuit%2C%20stabbing%20Shahzad%20several%20more%20times%20until%20he%20collapsed%2C%20dead.%20The%20killer%2C%20as%20though%20unaffected%2C%20returned%20calmly%20to%20the%20meat%20shop%2C%20picked%20up%20his%20order%20and%20walked%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20frantic%20calls%2C%20police%20officers%20soon%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20retrieved%20Shahzad's%20body%20and%20sent%20it%20for%20an%20autopsy.%20With%20no%20initial%20clues%20on%20the%20killer's%20identity%2C%20three%20teams%20were%20quickly%20mobilised%20to%20scour%20the%20area%20and%20examine%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20nearby%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20night%2C%20police%20received%20a%20tip-off%20about%20the%20accused%2C%20identified%20as%20Amarjeet%20Mahato%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bihar.%20Around%20dawn%20today%2C%20they%20traced%20Mahato%20to%20the%20jungle%20bordering%20Sector%20117.%20When%20police%20closed%20in%2C%20Mahato%20fired%20at%20the%20officers%20with%20a%20pistol.%20In%20the%20ensuing%20exchange%20of%20fire%2C%20Mahato%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%2C%20subdued%2C%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20The%20police%20also%20seized%20the%20knife%20used%20in%20Shahzad's%20murder%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Mahato's%20pistol%20and%20a%20stash%20of%20live%20cartridges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shahzad%20was%20the%20father%20of%20three%20children.%20His%20wife%20Salma%20works%20as%20a%20cook.%20Shahzad%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20driver%2C%20was%20hoping%20to%20secure%20new%20work%20when%20he%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20meat%20shop%20was%20equipped%20with%20surveillance%20cameras%2C%20the%20footage%20captured%20only%20glimpses%20of%20the%20attack%3A%20Shahzad%20is%20seen%20fleeing%20the%20shop%20after%20the%20initial%20stab%20wound%2C%20followed%20by%20Mahato%20in%20quick%20pursuit.%20The%20police%20have%20confiscated%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20surrounding%20shops%20as%20part%20of%20their%20ongoing%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGulzar%2C%20the%20meat%20shop's%20owner%2C%20vanished%20immediately%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731662280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3rlt9co_noida-murder-accused-_625x300_15_November_24.jpg%22%2