%20personal%20insights%20into%20his%20work%20ethic%2C%20revealing%20that%20throughout%20much%20of%20his%20career%2C%20he%20maintained%20an%20intense%20schedule%20of%2014-hour%20days%2C%20six%20and%20a%20half%20days%20a%20week.%20He%20would%20arrive%20at%20the%20office%20by%206%3A30%20am%20and%20leave%20at%20around%208%3A40%20pm.%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20proud%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20entrepreneur%20firmly%20believes%20hard%20work%20is%20the%20only%20path%20to%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20work%20hard%20in%20this%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20Even%20if%20you%20are%20the%20most%20intelligent%20guy%20you%20have%20to%20work%20hard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-on-70-hour-advice-you-have-to-be-productive-4865828%5C%22%3ENarayana%20Murthy%20On%20%26quot%3B70-Hour%26quot%3B%20Advice%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20Have%20To%20Be%20Productive%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20improve%20the%20delivery%20of%20public%20services%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20had%20a%20suggestion%20for%20PM%20Modi.%20He%20proposed%20that%20the%20government%20consider%20hiring%20more%20managers%20with%20formal%20training%20over%20administrators%20selected%20through%20the%20current%20civil%20services%20examination%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20candidate%20is%20selected%2C%20he%20or%20she%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20Mussoorie%20(where%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20Of%20Administration%20is%20located)%20for%20training%2C%20where%20he%20or%20she%20will%20be%20trained%20in%20specialised%20sector%20agriculture%2C%20defence%20or%20manufacturing%2C%20which%20is%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20current%20practice%20of%20creating%20general%20administrators%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20candidates%20will%20become%20subject%20matter%20experts%20once%20the%20training%20is%20over%20and%20serve%20the%20country%20in%20their%20respective%20fields%20for%2030-40%20years%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731660960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fb9na25qo_narayana-murthy_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwill-take-it-to-my-grave-narayana-murthy-doubles-down-on-70-hour-work-week-7023729%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%26quot%3B%20with%20India's%20shift%20from%20a%20six-day%20workweek%20to%20a%20five-day%20workweek%20in%201986.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwill-take-it-to-my-grave-narayana-murthy-doubles-down-on-70-hour-work-week-7023729%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20India%20need%20Jio%2C%20Paytm%2C%20Ola%20%26amp%3B%20Swiggy%2C%20Zerodha's%20Nithin%20Kamath%20'reshares'%202019%20statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731660830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115330074%2Cimgsize-14888.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fzerodha-founder-nithin-kamath-reshares-his-2019-statement-on-why-india-need-jio-paytm-ola-and-swiggy%2Farticleshow%2F115330083.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zerodha%20CEO%20Nithin%20Kamath%20celebrated%20the%20recent%20IPO%20of%20Swiggy%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%202019%20prediction%20about%20the%20growth%20of%20Indian%20tech%20startups.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20success%20of%20homegrown%20brands%20like%20Paytm%2C%20Ola%2C%20and%20Swiggy%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20Indian%20market%20and%20expressing%20hope%20for%20more%20IPOs%20from%20local%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdn