een%20fodder%2C%20ghee%2C%20soybeans%20and%20corn.%20This%20specialised%20diet%20ensures%20that%20Anmol%20is%20always%20prepared%20for%20exhibitions%20and%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol's%20health%20is%20also%20maintained%20through%20daily%20grooming.%20The%20buffalo%20is%20bathed%20twice%20a%20day.%20A%20special%20mixture%20of%20almond%20and%20mustard%20oil%20keeps%20its%20coat%20glossy%20and%20healthy.%20Despite%20the%20considerable%20expense%2C%20Gill%20is%20dedicated%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20care%20for%20Anmol%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20selling%20the%20buffalo's%20mother%20and%20sister%20in%20the%20past%20to%20cover%20the%20costs.%20Anmol's%20mother%20was%20known%20for%20producing%2025%20litres%20of%20milk%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anmol's%20impressive%20size%20and%20diet%20play%20a%20big%20part%20in%20its%20value%2C%20it%20is%20the%20buffalo's%20role%20in%20cattle%20breeding%20that%20truly%20drives%20its%20worth.%20Anmol's%20semen%2C%20collected%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20is%20in%20high%20demand%20among%20breeders.%20Each%20extraction%20is%20valued%20at%20Rs%20250%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20breed%20hundreds%20of%20cattle.%20The%20steady%20income%20from%20semen%20sales%20generates%20Rs%204-5%20lakh%20monthly%2C%20helping%20Gill%20manage%20the%20significant%20expenses%20of%20maintaining%20the%20buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20several%20lucrative%20offers%20to%20sell%20Anmol%20at%20its%20Rs%2023%20crore%20valuation%2C%20Gill%20sees%20Anmol%20as%20a%20family%20member%20and%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20parting%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731655500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fo07paqto_anmol-buffalo-_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-buffalo-worth-rs-23-crore-enjoys-a-royal-diet-and-almond-oil-massages-everyday-7024291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20buffalo%20in%20Haryana%2C%20valued%20at%20Rs%2023%20crore%2C%20i