ristocratic%20family%20on%20June%204%2C%201923%2C%20the%20princess%20was%2018%20when%20she%20married%20the%20younger%20brother%20of%20wartime%20emperor%20Hirohito.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20five%20children%20--%20two%20girls%20and%20three%20boys.%20She%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20first%2C%20a%20daughter%2C%20in%201944%20during%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imperial%20couple's%20house%20burned%20down%20in%20an%20air%20raid%20and%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20shelter%20with%20her%20baby%2C%20according%20to%20Japan's%20Asahi%20Shimbun%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHirohito%20--%20who%20served%20as%20Japan's%20commander-in-chief%20during%20its%20brutal%20march%20across%20Asia%20in%20the%201930s%20and%2040s%20--%20surrendered%20in%20an%20August%201945%20speech%2C%20after%20the%20United%20States%20dropped%20atomic%20bombs%20on%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Mikasa's%20husband%20Prince%20Mikasa%2C%20who%20died%20in%202016%20at%20100%2C%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20decision%20to%20end%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20young%20officers%20who%20disagreed%20would%20come%20regularly%20to%20the%20shelter%20to%20try%20and%20change%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Mikasa%20recalled%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20frightening%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bheated%20arguments%20and%20tension%2C%20as%20if%20bullets%20were%20about%20to%20fly%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Asahi%20Shimbun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lost%20their%20home%2C%20the%20decades%20that%20followed%20were%20far%20from%20luxurious%20for%20the%20princess%2C%20who%20took%20on%20domestic%20duties%20as%20the%20family%20struggled%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20raising%20my%20children%2C%20Japanese%20society%20was%20still%20in%20a%20difficult%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20her%20100th%20birthday%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Imperial%20Household%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recall%20with%20deep%20gratitude%20how%20many%20people%2C%20including%20my%20husband%2C%20always%20supported%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20princess%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20of%20Princess%20Misaka's%20sons%20passed%20away%20before%20her%2C%20including%20one%20who%20died%20aged%2047%20while%20playing%20squash%20at%20the%20Canadian%20embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale-only%20succession%20rules%20mean%20that%20Japan's%20royal%20women%20cannot%20ascend%20to%20the%20throne%20and%20must%20forgo%20their%20imperial%20status%20if%20they%20marry%20outside%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Misaka%20has%20three%20granddaughters%20who%20remain%20princesses%2C%20including%20Akiko%2C%20whose%202015%20book%20was%20a%20hit%20in%20Japan%2C%20describing%20her%20studies%20at%20Oxford%20and%20an%20incident%20in%20which%20her%20diplomatic%20passport%20caused%20suspicion%20at%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20101-year-old's%20passing%20followed%20reports%20since%20early%20November%20that%20her%20condition%20had%20begun%20to%20deteriorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrent%20Emperor%20Naruhito's%2018-year-old%20nephew%20Prince%20Hisahito%20is%20the%20only%20young%20heir%20to%20the%20throne.%20Naruhito's%20daughter%20Princess%20Aiko%20is%20barred%20from%20the%20throne%20under%20the%20Imperial%20Household%20Law%2C%20in%20place%20since%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731651000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F6b1mue3o_japan-princess-mikasa_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprincess-mikasa-oldest-member-of-japans-royal-family-dies-at-101-7024151%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Princess%20Mikasa%2C%20the%20oldest%20member%20of%20Japan's%20royal%20family%20and%20great%20aunt%20to%20the%20e