0years%2C%20he%20collaborated%20with%20event%20organisers%20across%20the%20state%20and%20worked%20with%20institutions%20like%20the%20Mehrangarh%20Trust%20and%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20actively%20providing%20platforms%20for%20folk%20artists%20to%20showcase%20their%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Bhati%2C%20along%20with%20Sharon%20Genevive%2C%20launched%20%E2%80%98BlueCity%20Walls%E2%80%99%2C%20through%20which%20they%20collaborated%20with%20artists%2C%20organised%20shows%2C%20and%20conducted%20tours%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287963%2Firish-man-revives-cleans-stepwells-in-jodhpur-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Jodhpur%E2%80%99s%20old%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20employing%20local%20residents%20in%20the%20process.%20As%20their%20work%20with%20artists%20progressed%2C%20the%20couple%20realised%20that%20much%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20was%20slowly%20fading%20away.%20With%20the%20older%20generation%20passing%20on%2C%20the%20younger%20generation%20lacked%20a%20formal%20way%20to%20learn%20and%20preserve%20these%20traditional%20art%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202750px)%20100vw%2C%202750px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bringing%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20to%20life%3A%20Children%20and%20musicians%20from%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20unite%20in%20harmony%2C%20preserving%20and%20celebrating%20their%20cultural%20heritage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03486-1_11zon-1731068934.jpg%202750w%2C%20https%