ered%20with%20skin).%20Same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20%3Cem%3Esarangi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20stringed%20instrument%20played%20with%20a%20bow)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealghoza%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emorchang%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Bhati%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthani%20band%20went%20viral%20on%20Netflix%2C%20reviving%20folk%20music%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhati%20soon%20initiated%20projects%20to%20bring%20young%20Rajasthani%20voices%20to%20the%20cultural%20forefront.%20His%20first%20major%20success%20was%20the%20band%20%3Cem%3ERaitila%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20comprising%20seven%20to%20eight%20young%20men%20from%20folk%20music%20backgrounds.%20They%20trained%20and%20rehearsed%20for%20about%20six%20months%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20debut%20song%20%3Cem%3EMehman%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20composed%20and%20arranged%20by%20Bhati%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20track%20gained%20immense%20popularity%2C%20even%20being%20featured%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20popular%20Netflix%20show%20%3Cem%3EMismatched%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20it%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20next%20project%20%3Cem%3EKaisariya%20Rajasthan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereceived%20similar%20response.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20basically%20created%20bands%20and%20albums%20that%20have%20their%20own%20identity%2C%20not%20just%20that%20of%20folk%20music%20but%20of%20true%20Rajasthani%20artists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203672px)%20100vw%2C%203672px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Musicians%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20unite%20on%20stage%2C%20sharing%20the%20soul%20of%20folk%20music%20with%20a%20captivated%20audience.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098.jpg%203672w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375566%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20folk%20artists%20have%20not%20been%20given%20their%20due%20diligence%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20certain%20perception%20people%20have%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20folk%20artists.%20If%20you%20go%20to%20an%20event%20organiser%20and%20say%20you%20have%20some%20folk%20artists%20who%E2%80%99d%20love%20to%20perform%2C%20the%20artist%20fee%20immediately%20cuts%20in%20half%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20funds%20are%20coming%20from%20a%20private%20organisation%20or%20the%20Government.%20What%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20these%20initial%20projects%20gained%20enough%20traction%2C%20Bhati%20and%20his%20team%20kept%20meeting%20new%20people%20and%20patrons%20who%20wanted%20to%20help.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20got%20our%20footing%20right%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20these%20artists%E2%80%99%20development%20also.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artists%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fully%20funded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartist%20residency%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20young%20children%20from%20across%20Rajasthan%20can%20gather%20to%20learn%20folk%20music%20from%20maestros%20and%20gurus.%20This%20initiative%20is%20groundbreaking%20because%2C%20unlike%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20educational%20structure%20for%20folk%20music.%20Traditionally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20orally%20through%20generations%2C%20with%20no%20written%20records%20to%20preserve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20spans%20seven%20days%20and%20includes%20nine%20classes%20covering%20various%20disciplines%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20vocals%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekamaicha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emurli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flute)%2C%20%3Cem%3Etandura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamboura)%2C%20and%20more.%20Currently%2C%20the%20programme%20works%20with%20three%20folk%20music%20communities%3A%20%3Cem%3ELanga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EManganiyars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20of%20these%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20dignitaries%20like%20Lakha%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20and%20the%20maestro%20of%20Sarangi%2C%20give%20masterclasses%20here.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20to%20foreign%20countries%20or%20even%20other%20states%20to%20play%2C%20the%20reception%20is%20good%20because%20the%20type%20of%20people%20who%20come%20to%20watch%20us%20actually%20value%20folk%20singing.%20So%2C%20people%20do%20like%20it.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20to%20actually%20teach%20kids%20and%20make%20them%20understand%20what%20it%20means%20because%20only%20then%20will%20this%20art%20be%20able%20to%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203269px)%20100vw%2C%203269px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223269%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20from%20the%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20learning%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201.jpg%203269w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375568%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20also%20promotes%20community%20building%2C%20addressing%20the%20longstanding%20divisions%20between%20different%20folk%20music%20communities.%20Traditionally%2C%20these%20groups%20rarely%20interact%20or%20share%20performance%20spaces%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20palpable%20sense%20of%20hostility.%20However%2C%20by%20bringing%20the%20younger%20generation%20together%20in%20a%20shared%20learning%20environment%2C%20the%20programme%20helps%20break%20down%20these%20barriers%2C%20fostering%20mutual%20respect%20and%20collaboration%20as%20they%20freely%20interact%20and%20learn%20from%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20in%20our%20villages%2C%20artists%20would%20interact%20with%20each%20other%20at%20cultural%20events%20and%20weddings%2C%20where%20they%20would%20get%20to%20play%20night%20after%20night.%20But%20that%20system%20has%20ended%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20residency%20took%20place%20in%20Pokhran%2C%20with%20support%20from%20BlueCity%20Walls%2C%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20and%20some%20anonymous%20funders.%20Speaking%20with%20Rakshat%20Hooja%2C%20the%20current%20head%20of%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%20%3C%2Fem%