by%20to%20him.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20I%20also%20started%20with%20organic%20farming%20on%20my%20terrace.%20The%20first%20thing%20I%20grew%20were%20chillies%2C%20and%20they%20turned%20out%20really%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20months%20later%2C%20he%20came%20across%20hydroponics%2C%20a%20method%20of%20growing%20plants%20in%20nutrient-rich%20water%20instead%20of%20soil%20and%20decided%20to%20start%20incorporating%20it%20into%20his%20little%20terrace%20farm.%20However%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356971%2Fhydroponics-farming-without-soil-sustainable-agriculture-farmer-increases-income-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20still%20nascent%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20there%20were%20barely%20any%20resources%20available.%20Most%20information%20on%20the%20internet%20was%20tailored%20to%20other%20countries%2C%20their%20climate%2C%20their%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20that%2C%20the%20humid%20climate%20of%20Kerala%20presented%20another%20obstacle.%20%E2%80%9CTemperature%20control%20was%20a%20significant%20issue.%20It%20would%20often%20reach%2038%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20my%20roof%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20protect%20my%20nutrient%20solution%20from%20heating%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201715px)%20100vw%2C%201715px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FDSC03601_11zon-1730966227.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221715%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20a%20digital%20sensor%20system%20monitoring%20temperature%20and%20humidit