g.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%20but%20I%20did%20know%20what%20%E2%80%98not%E2%80%99%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20course%20on%20social%20design%20offered%20by%20Ambedkar%20University%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was%20then.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20time%20hearing%20the%20term%2C%20but%20the%20design%20aspect%20intrigued%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20combination%20of%20%E2%80%98social%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98design%E2%80%99%20piqued%20my%20curiosity%2C%20so%20I%20applied%20for%20the%20course.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20step%20outside%20the%20classroom%20and%20engage%20directly%20with%20people%2C%20seeking%20real-world%20solutions%20to%20everyday%20problems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20a%20younger%20Ittisha%20from%20Guwahati%2C%20Assam%2C%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20nine%20years%20later%20she%20would%20be%20living%20in%20a%20rented%20house%20in%20Sangti%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20working%20alongside%20villagers%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20living%20in%20the%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201476px)%20100vw%2C%201476px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221476%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ittisha%20celebrates%20a%20clean%20Sangti%20with%20the%20community's%20young%20environmentalists%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796.jpg%201476w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIttisha-with-Mon-Stars_11zon-1730809796-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-374408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221107%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIttisha%20celebrates%20a%20clean%20Sangti%20with%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20young%20environmentalists%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20Ittisha%20in%20Delhi%20while%20giving%20a%20talk%20on%20%E2%80%98Ride%20to%20Light%E2%80%99%20%5Ba%20fundraiser%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F315646%2Fmerwyn-coutinho-rajiv-rathod-batti-kits-electricity-in-arunachal-pradesh-remote-villages-video%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Batti%20Project%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20explained%20how%20we%20were%20generating%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Merwyn%20Coutinho%2C%20co-founder%20of%20The%20Batti%20Project%2C%20under%20the%20Further%20and%20Beyond%20Foundation%2C%20which%20has%20illuminated%20several%20remote%20villages%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20we%20told%20people%20about%20our%20work%20with%20The%20Batti%20Project%20in%20Arunachal%20and%20mentioned%20that%20we%20might%20need%20support.%20Instead%20of%20asking%20for%20donations%2C%20we%20encouraged%20them%20to%20contribute%20by%20donating%20their%20electronic%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20Ittisha%20had%20chosen%20e-waste%20as%20the%20subject%20for%20her%20dissertation.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20people%20were%20researching%20electronic%20waste%20at%20that%20time.%20So%20I%20would%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20papers%20and%20then%20try%20to%20identify%20places%20where%20electronic%20waste%20recycling%20is%20happening%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi.%20Then%20I%20would%20go%20out%20onto%20the%20field%20to%20locate%20the%20places%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20exposing%20her%20to%20e-waste%2C%20her%20on-ground%20work%20during%20her%20thesis%20also%20exposed%20her%20to%20solid%20waste%20and%20the%20many%20problems%20it%20brings%20along%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20per%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments1.worldbank.org%2Fcurated%2Fen%2F823241618991659221%2Fpdf%2FIndia-Sustainable-Solid-Waste-Management-in-Mountain-Areas.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Bank%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20waste%20generation%20in%20India%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20388.77%20million%20tonnes%20a%20year%20by%202030.%20The%20ecologically%20sensitive%20Indian%20Himalayan%20Region%20(IHR)%20that%20stretches%20from%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20West%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20East%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20challenges%20this%20may%20bring.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20reveals%20that%20municipal%20solid%20waste%20generation%20in%20IHR%20is%20approximately%2014%2C450%20tonnes%20per%20day%20or%20over%205.2%20million%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20A%20majority%20of%20this%20problem%20plagues%20urban%20centres%2C%20but%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20tourism%20and%20development%20to%20cater%20to%20it%2C%20this%20number%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20exponentially%20in%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20completing%20her%20dissertation%2C%20Ittisha%20decided%20to%20start%20something%20to%20address%20this%20problem%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20states.%20She%20partnered%20with%20Merwyn%20and%20Rajiv%2C%20initially%20working%20for%20The%20Batti%20Project%2C%20and%20soon%20establishing%20the%20Northeast%20Waste%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProject%20Sangti%3A%20A%20community%20takes%20charge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20journey%20to%20Sangti%20began%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ittisha%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CA%20friend%20who%20runs%20a%20travel%20company%2C%20which%20was%20just%20starting%20out%20at%20the%20time%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20ask%20for%20my%20help.%E2%80%9D%20She%20was%20given%20the%20role%20of%20tour%20instructor%2C%20leading%20a%20group%20of%20school%20students%20to%20a%20summer%20camp.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20something%20about%20this%20place%20%E2%80%94%20it%20felt%20like%20%3Cem%3Edeja%20vu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20river%2C%20the%20valley%2C%20the%20fields%2C%20everything%20seemed%20familiar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20even%20here%2C%20waste%20was%20a%20noticeable%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20background%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345419%2Fbiogas-startup-greeneria-renewable-technology-turns-wet-waste-into-fuel-for-rashtrapati-bhavan-microsoft-hp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20social%20design%2C%20Ittisha%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20react%20to%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20she%20witnessed%20in%20Sangti.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20could%20do%20was%20conduct%20a%20cleanup%20drive%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20kids.%20For%20the%20village%2C%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20thing%20was%20happening%2C%20where%20outsiders%20were%20coming%20and%20picking%20up%20their%20trash%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202511px)%20100vw%2C%202